Body: Description: Members of a department require login access to Fedline for regulatory work. Disabling CAP resolves the issue but when checking logs there are no blocks for this website shown.

What We've Learned Updated: created DPI allowlist for the blocked websites and added it to the policy
enabled stealthy dpi driver
Next Steps Updated: waiting for the customer to test
